<subsection>
Real-time system connections

orbafter orb time
    Set the orb read pointer to the first packet after specified time

orbclients orb
    Return a handle to status information for clients of the specified orb

orbclientsfree clients_handle
    Frees the clients information referenced by the specified handle

orbclose orb
    Close an orb connection for the specified orb descriptor

orbgetclient clients_handle index ?options?
    Returns client information for the specified client in the clients_handle
