orbgetdatasources orb
    Returns a list of data source names from the specified orb

orbgetnclients clients_handle
    Returns the number of individual clients referenced by the clients_handle

orbgetnsources sources_handle
    Returns the number of individual sources referenced by the sources_handle

orbgetsource sources_handle index ?options?
    Returns source information for the indexed source
