orbhelp 
    Print synopsis lines for orb Tcl commands

orbopen orbname permission
    Open an orb connection

orbpffree pf_handle
    Frees the parameter file object referenced by pf_handle

orbpfget pf_handle name
    returns the value for parameter name from the referenced pf_handle

orbping orb
    Returns the version number of the specified orb

orbpktchanfree packet_handle
    Free the specified unstuffed packet-channel

orbpktchangetcd1 packetchan_handle
    Returns CD1 status information for CD-1-format packet channels

orbpktchangethdr packetchan_handle
    Returns packet-channel header information

orbpktfree packet_handle
    Frees the orb packet referenced by the packet_handle

orbpktgetdb packet_handle dbptr
    Returns a database pointer pointing to the row in the referenced /db/.*orb packet

orbpktgethdr packet_handle
    Return a list of generic packet header information for the referenced packet

orbpktgetlog packet_handle
    Returns log messages from the referenced /log/.*orb packet

orbpktgetpf packet_handle
    returns a pf_handle reference from the referenced /pf/.*orb packet

orbpktgetqtping packet_handle
    Returns a string with the response to a qt2orb ping command

orbpktgetstatus packet_handle
    Returns a string with qt2orb status information

orbpktunstuffdata packet_handle
    Unstuff an orb packet referenced by packet_handle, returning a list of unstuffed packet channels

orbqtpingsend orb
    Sends a ping command to qt2orb via the specified command-orb

orbqtshell qtshell_handle
    Handle qtshell through orb 

orbqtshellfree qtshell_handle
    Free a quanterra shell handle 

orbqtshellstart cmdorbname netsta cmd
    Start a quanterra shell 

orbreap reap_handle
    Read a new orb packet from a previously started reap thread, returning a packet handle

orbreapstart orb [block]
    Start reaping (reading) packets from orb, returning a read handle.

orbseek orb whence
    set the orb read pointer, returning the new read-position packet id.

orbselect orb selectexpr
    Select sources to read from an orb, returning the number of matches

orbsources orb
    Reads status information for sources of orb, returning a handle

orbsourcesfree sources_handle
    Frees the sources information referenced by the specified handle

orbstat orb ?options?
    Returns requested status information for the specified orb
